item.title: How do i open client.java?
item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

That is now what he is trying to ask.

EIDT:

  1. google.com
  2. search “java decompiler”
  3. Download a java -decompiler
  4. Open it
  5. File > Open Choose the client.class file
  6. File > Save As > Click Ok
  7. You now have a client.java
